description: Flame Brothers Pizza is the very first and only Neopolitan-style gourmet pizza truck in Los Angeles! Here are our promises:1. Fast cooking: under 2 minutes from scratch to finish!2. The best crust you'll ever have, due to the 1400 degree oven!3. The best ingredients; only fresh mozzarella cheese and caputo 00 dough, house-made sausage and meatballs!4. Healthy old dough which is easier for people to digest!Stop by Flame Brothers for the best pizza around!
name: Flame Pizza Brothers
